16 core fields total (10 must-have + 6 good-to-have), each consumed by ≥1 module. "Required" enforced at app layer only. `gender` = text + CHECK constraint (not enum). `updated_at` set explicitly by app code, no DB trigger.

**recovery_items** (one row per item, not per user) — not yet built. id, user_id (FK), item_type (CHECK: medicine/test/report_reminder), medicine_name, dosage, frequency, test_name, scheduled_date, end_date (medicine only), completed (bool, default false), created_at.

