## DROPDOWN / CHECKLIST VOCABULARY

**Gender:** Male / Female / Other / Prefer not to disclose

**Family History & Existing Conditions** — shared 15-item checklist (identical list, only question framing differs):
1. Diabetes (Type 1 or 2) 2. Hypertension 3. Heart Disease 4. Stroke 5. Cancer (any type) 6. Kidney Disease 7. Liver Disease 8. Thyroid Disorder 9. Asthma/Respiratory Condition 10. Obesity 11. Arthritis/Joint Disorders 12. Mental Health Condition (Depression, Anxiety, etc.) 13. PCOS/PCOD 14. Migraine/Chronic Headaches 15. None of the above

**"None of the above" behavior (frozen):** disable-on-select. Checking "None" disables/unchecks the other 14; checking any other option unchecks "None." Built once as a shared, reusable checklist component — used for both `family_history` and `existing_conditions`. No free-text "Other" option.

**City coverage (frontend only):** profile city input may offer Metropolitan / Rural as options for UX completeness. Has zero effect on matching today — every policy's `city_tier` is `"Both"`.

