## MATCHING LOGIC — GENERIC MEDICINE ALTERNATIVES

Direct DB lookup only, no AI: `WHERE medicine_name ILIKE '%input%' OR brand_manufacturer ILIKE '%input%'`. No match → static "data not available." No fallback tiers.

